{"name":"adv-file-append-var","expect":"block","command":"echo \"$x\" >> log.txt","reason":"追記も同様"}
{"name":"adv-devnull-then-file","expect":"block","command":"echo \"$(date)\" > /dev/null; echo \"$(date)\" > f.txt","reason":"デバイス破棄が混ざっても後続のファイルリダイレクトはブロック"}
{"name":"adv-dev-nullx-lookalike","expect":"block","command":"echo \"$x\" > /dev/nullx","reason":"/dev/null の見せかけ (末尾境界) は除外しない"}
{"name":"adv-redirect-into-subst","expect":"block","command":"echo x > \"$(which claude)\"","reason":"置換結果への書き込み (バイナリ上書き) は除外2 の対象外"}
{"name":"adv-which-dotcodex","expect":"block","command":"touch \"$(which .codex)\" > /dev/null","reason":"先頭ドットの WORD は除外せず .codex 参照判定が効く"}
{"name":"adv-revparse-dotarg","expect":"block","command":"echo x $(git rev-parse .codex) > out.log","reason":"ドット入り引数の rev-parse は除外しない"}
